<div type="description" n="monument">
<head>Description of Monument</head>
<p><rs type="material">White marble</rs> <rs type="objectType">seat</rs>ing along the edge of pool.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="text">
<head>Description of Text</head>
<p>Inscribed roughly on the upper face. i: Beside the design. ii: Texts are cut outside the frame; a. Along east edge. b. Along north edge; deeper letters, ave. 0.06. the text apparently continued on an adjacent block, now lost. c. Along west edge. d. Along south edge.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="letters">
<head>Letters</head>
<p>i: shallow letters, <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.05(ο) - 0.07</measure>; cursive mu, lunate sigma. ii.a very worn, ave. <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.04</measure>. ii.b deeper letters, ave. <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.06</measure>; lunate sigma. ii.c: <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.035</measure>. ii.d: <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.04</measure>, lunate sigma (very unclear). iii: very faint, <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.02-0.05</measure>.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="date">
<head>Date</head>
<p>
<date exact="none" notAfter="1000" notBefore="0101">Second-tenth century A.D.</date> (<rs type="criteria">context</rs>)</p>
</div>
